<html>
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>

        :root {
            --blue: #1e90ff;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --darkblue: #0A2647;
            --darkblue2: #144272;
            --darkblue3: #2C74B3;
            --black: #1A0000;
            --fullblue: #1C315E;
            --gray: #282A3A;
            --gray1: #3F4E4F;
            --gray2: #7F8487;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: var(--darkblue);
            border-width: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .fa {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 30px;
            width: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            .fa:hover {
                opacity: 0.7;
            }

        .fa-facebook {
            background: #3B5998;
            color: white;
        }

        .fa-twitter {
            background: #55ACEE;
            color: white;
        }

        .fa-google {
            background: #dd4b39;
            color: white;
        }

        .fa-linkedin {
            background: #007bb5;
            color: white;
        }

        .fa-youtube {
            background: #bb0000;
            color: white;
        }

        .fa-instagram {
            background: #125688;
            color: white;
        }

        }

        li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-style: normal;
            height: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-style: oblique;
        }

        .dropbtn {
            font-style: normal;
            height: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: var(--fullblue);
        }

            .navbar a {
                float: left;
                display: block;
                color: var(--white);
                text-align: center;
                padding: 15px;
                font-style: normal;
                font-size: 25px;
            }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 5px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            border-style: solid;
        }

        .dropbtn {
            background-color: var(--darkblue3);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .dropdown-content {
            position: absolute;
            background-color: var(--gray2);
            min-width: 5px;
            display: none;
        }

            .dropdown-content a {
                color: black;
                padding: 10px 12px;
                float: none;
                text-decoration: none;
                display: block;
                text-align: left;
            }




                .dropdown-content a:hover {
                    background-color: var(--darkblue3);
                }

        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {
            display: block;
        }

        .dropdown:hover .dropbtn {
            background-color: var(--gray2);
        }

        /* Accordion to*/

        .accordion {
            background-color: dimgray;
            color: #444;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 18px;
            width: 50%;
            border: none;
            text-align: left;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: 0.4s;
            color: var(--blue1);
            margin: 5px;
        }

            .active, .accordion:hover {
                background-color: yellow;
            }

            .accordion:after {
                content: '\002B';
                color: var(--black);
                font-weight: bold;
                float: right;
                margin-left: 5px;
            }

        .active:after {
            content: "\2212";
        }

        .panel {
            padding: 0 18px;
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.2s ease-out;
        }

        .p1 {
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            width: 50%;
        }

        .dep {
            color: yellow;
            font-size: 30px;
            background-color: var(--black);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5px;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .further {
            color: yellow;
            background-color: black;
            padding: 5px;
            margin: 5px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .accorimg {
            float: right;
            border: double;
            background-color: var(--darkblue);
        }
    </style>
    <title>
        Faculty of Sciences
    </title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Faculty of Sciences</h1>
    <div class="p1">
        The faculty of sciences envisions to provide theoretical as well as practicalknowledge with quality
        research and innovation to develop highly skilled professionals in demanding fields of physical and
        biological sciences particularly in food, agriculture , pharmaceutical, forensic and medical sciences.
    </div>
    <h2>Our Goals</h2>
    <dov class="p1">
        Faculty of Sciences also aims to develop interdeciplinary insight, practical knowledge and emperical
        skills among students. Moreover, faculty of science is committed for the professional and personal
        growth of students through the development of new scientific knowledge and interpersonal skills.
        We strive to provide ample opportunities for professional and personal growth of our students that will allow
        students to excel in future endeavors
    </dov>
    <div class="drop">
        <div class="dep">Our Departments</div>
        <div class="accorimg">
            <img src="~/image/picture1.jpg" alt="image" width="650" height="400" />
        </div>
        <button class="accordion">Department of Biochemistry</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p> The Department of Biochemistry discovers and transfers new knowledge about the molecular basis of life through basic biomolecular science, research and cross-disciplinary knowledge transfer and trainings.</p>
            <a href="~/home/Addmission"><button type="button" class="further">Further Information -->> </button></a>

        </div>


        <button class="accordion">Department of Biological science</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>  Department of Biological Sciences provides a unique opportunity to the students for studying all the aspects of modern biology. </p>
            <a href="~/home/Addmission"><button type="button" class="further">Further Information -->> </button></a>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Department of BioTechnology</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p> Department of Biotechnology is one of the leading departments in the Faculty of Sciences with an extensive number of career opportunities in the modern world.</p>
            <a href="~/home/Addmission"><button type="button" class="further">Further Information -->> </button></a>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Department of Chemistry</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p> The Department of Chemistry of USKT aspires to excel in modern trends of Chemistry, research and services.</p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Department of Mathematics</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p> To develop mathematical curiosity in students and urge them to use inductive and deductive reasoning while solving problems.</p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Department of Physics</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>  The BS and MS program at the department of physics is highly focused to inculcate the sense for search and research starting at very basic level.</p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">Department of Zoology</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>  The Department of Zoology strives for quality education in Zoology and excellence in animal sciences by delivering basic and applied knowledge.</p>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script>
        var acc = document.getElementsByClassName("accordion");
        var i;

        for (i = 0; i < acc.length; i++) {
          acc[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
            this.classList.toggle("active");
            var panel = this.nextElementSibling;
            if (panel.style.maxHeight) {
              panel.style.maxHeight = null;
            } else {
              panel.style.maxHeight = panel.scrollHeight + "px";
            }
          });
        }
    </script>


</body>
</html>